data.description: Welcome home! This is your chance to become the proud owner of this charming property nestled in the gorgeous Crossing Community. You are greeted by an exquisite curb appeal featuring a convenient 1-car garage and a front yard displaying an impressive mature tree. Explore inside to discover ample living spaces adorned with gleaming wood-look flooring, a designer color palette throughout, and striking vaulted ceilings. The well-kept kitchen boasts wood cabinetry, plenty of counter space, and built-in appliances ready for all your culinary adventures. The cozy bedrooms offer generously sized closets for easy organization. You will definitely love the two extra bedrooms located in the fully finished garden level basement, providing a calm and quiet retreat. Washer and dryer convey! Take advantage of the gas water heater, swamp cooler, and 1-year-old roof. Enjoy morning breakfast or evening relaxation in the lovely deck leading to the backyard, where you will also find great potential for adding your personal touch! What are you waiting for? Create new memories in this fantastic home!!
